               <msContents>
                  <summary>Praises of Mary, ውዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡; Gate of Light, አንቀጸ፡ ብርሃን፡; Image of Mary, Mälk‘a Maryam, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡; Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡ ኢየሱስ፡; Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡; Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
